    "Some emerging work has begun to explore marketing in the Metaverse.",
    "Ahn et al. (2022) studied advertising in the Metaverse by analyzing the relationship among consumers, media, and participation behavior.",
    "They proposed a bifold triadic relationships model to help readers understand the role of advertising in the Metaverse and its impact on consumer behavior.",
    "In the Metaverse, real-time multi-sensory social interaction (RMSI) between people is an important way of communication.",
    "Through theoretical logic and extensive field experiments, Hennig-Thurau et al. (2023) found that accessing the virtual world by VR headsets as part of RMSI can generate more interactive values than the 2-dimensional Internet."
